Decision/Capital Fund Inc saidentities associated with Mario Gabelli, an arbitrager, haveacquired 9.98 pct of the shares in a friendly transaction.    In a 13D filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission,The Gabelli Group Inc of New York, said it acquired 200,000shares of the fund in stock exchange transactions on March 25"in the ordinary course of business and not to acquire control"of the fund.    Decision has said it will seek shareholder approval toconvert to an operating company. It also plans to acquireHopper, Soliday and Co Inc, a regional stock brokerage. Reuter&#3;